||~ **Name/Designation**||~ **Synopsis**||~ **Access Type/s**||~ **Justification**||
||= SCP-5759||A series of entries on the **SCiPNet** database that anomalously appeared on  █/██/████.||Access to all documentation; use of anomaly; use of database slot "SCP-5759".||Anomaly could be modified for the purpose of **##a02c2c |PROJECT VISHAAK##**.||
